code: @Override public boolean equals(Object o) {     if (this == o) {         return true.     }     if (o == null || getClass() != o.getClass()) {         return false.     }     Pair<?> that = (Pair<?>) o.     return Objects.equals(left, that.left) && Objects.equals(right, that.right). }
@Override public int hashCode() {     return Objects.hash(left, right). }
@Override public String toString() {     return "(" + left + ", " + right + ")". }
